                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>A Shady friend - for Torrid days -</l>
                    <l>Is easier to find - </l>
                    <l>Than one of higher temperature </l>
                    <l>For Frigid - hour of mind - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The Vane a little to the East -</l>
                    <l>Scares Muslin souls - away - </l>
                    <l>If Broadcloth Hearts are<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 firmer </l>
                    <l>Than those of Organdy - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Who is to blame?<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 The Weaver?  </l>
                    <l>Ah, the bewildering thread!</l>
                    <l>The Tapestries of Paradise </l>
                    <l>So notelessly - are made!  </l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
